<div id="review_3387042578" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3387042578" />
    <a title="Stefan Stojanovski" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/55889357-stefan-stojanovski"><img alt="Stefan Stojanovski" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1589760154p2/55889357.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3387042578?book_show_action=true">Jun 12, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Stefan Stojanovski" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Stefan Stojanovski" href="/user/show/55889357-stefan-stojanovski">Stefan Stojanovski</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/55889357-stefan-stojanovski?shelf=read-for-class">read-for-class</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3387042578" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5849483168367413408">Iconic. <br/><br/>Every character was just in such misery. Oenone was a total G and tried her best to be a friend, although subtextually maybe even more than that. Phèdre was just an icon. And every other icon was also very well written.<br/><br/>It had great writing and I loved the plot and the ancient Greek influence.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


